imit storefront and administrator area access to certain IP-addresses with different options','en'),('banners','Banners management','Allows you to create text and visual banners','en'),('watermarks','Watermarks','Allows you to add watermarks to product and category images','en'),('discussion','Comments and reviews','Lets customers leave comments to categories, pages, etc., review vendors and write testimonials','en'),('product_reviews','Product reviews','Allows your customers to leave reviews for products. That can build up trust, provide social proof, and add user-generated content to your site.','en'),('wishlist','Wish List','Lets customers store items in personal wish lists','en'),('image_zoom','Image zoom','Shows zoomed image on product image hover','en'),('google_sitemap','Google sitemap','Creates a sitemap.xml for Google','en'),('required_products','Required products','Makes it possible to specify products required for purchase','en'),('data_feeds','Data feeds','Makes it possible to create product data feeds in CSV','en'),('price_list','Price list','Generates configurable price list in PDF or XLS','en'),('catalog_mode','Catalog mode','Allows you to use the store as a product catalog','en'),('hybrid_auth','Social login','Adds the Social Login feature; allows customers use Facebook, Twitter, etc. to log in on the store','en'),('janrain','Janrain','Adds the Social Login feature; allows customers use Facebook, Twitter, etc. to log in on the store','en'),('rus_hybrid_auth','Social Login: Russian Social Networks','Adds the support of Russian social networks to the Social Login add-on','en'),('zapier','Integration with Zapier','Allows you to integrate CS-Cart with over 4 000 other apps through Zapier.','en'),('price_per_unit','Price per unit','Allows you to display price per unit on catalog and product pages.','en'),('rus_russianpost','Russian localization — Russian post','Calculation of shipping cost: Russian Post and EMS Russian Post. Printing of Russian post forms.','en'),('rus_ruble','Russian localization — Russian ruble and currencies sync','Updating currency rates according to Central Bank of Russia','en'),('rus_payments','Russian localization — Russian payments','Payments: Assist, Yandex.Checkpoint, Webmoney, Sberbank, PayAnyWay, PayMaster, RBK, Vkredit24.ru, Avangard, Payler','en'),('robokassa','Robokassa','Allows you to accept payments via Robokassa','en'),('rus_sberbank','Russian localization — Sberbank','Payment acceptance via Sberbank Online','en'),('rus_personal_data_processing','Consent for personal data processing (Russian Federal Law 152)','Lets you ask for customers\' consent for personal data processing in accordance with the Russian Federal Law 152.','en'),('gdpr','GDPR Compliance (EU)','Helps you to comply with GDPR (a European Union regulation on personal data) by showing customers info about their personal data, asking their consent for its processing, and by offering ways to delete or export personal data.','en'),('shopify_import','Import from Shopify','Allows you to import products from Shopify.','en'),('my_changes','My Changes (example add-on)','A dummy add-on to let devs see how add-ons work. You can also use it to introduce small changes not worthy of a separate add-on','en'),('tech_support_chat','Techical support chat','Adds live chat with the technical support team int the Administration panel','en');
